[SN]TITLE[SN]
Uninsured Lamborghini seized near police station in Cambridge

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An uninsured Lamborghini sports car was seized after being stopped outside a police station.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Cambridgeshire police saw the Huracan model near to the force's base in Parkside, Cambridge, on Sunday.
